        "position": 3,
        "title": "DON’T BUY this product!!!",
        "text": "This product looked great when I got it. But quickly went down hill from there. FIRST ISSUE: Within 5 days the door that was put together by the factory lost its hinge. This cannot be fixed by us. It is within the gate/door so the screw is inside the poll. The other parts are assembled by the purchaser. If the screws come out you can put them back in. The gate can’t be fixed. So we only can get the dog out of the top now. This is a huge issue. I have 1 puppy. But when he’s too big to pick up how will I get him out? The cage will be unusable then. SECOND ISSUE: the paint started falling off just within having it two weeks. Again I have a small PUPPY that is all that’s in the cage. It doesn’t chew the metal. The paint is just falling off. THIRD ISSUE: The metal is rusting already. The rust is coming through. It is only a month at this time of rusting. It’s disappointing and Amazon says I am out of the window to return it. Don’t buy this product!!! IMAGES SHOW BROKEN HING THAT CANNOT BE FIXED. And RUST ALL JUST WITH A WEEK OR TWO.",
